{"tid":574694,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚又可以睇牙朗瘋狂入波了","createTime":"2018-02-27T15:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T19:32:44.000Z","uid":36310,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e86cddd2e21db0d2bbdeca4f4a57ebc3246d2718","tid":574694,"uid":36310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:19:56.000Z","msg":"牙朗一發力可以屌打美欺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe55f6ebe1629779b87c6da9aacfe46d2a0377e","tid":574694,"uid":122740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:21:07.000Z","msg":"點知呀朗話要無限做波俾賓9入"},{"pid":"e34b4e7c6f1f2f5950da5a84b76407feba4c1722","tid":574694,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:21:44.000Z","msg":"私家G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c231457f93204ed6370f3a5a85be208ddb92d03","tid":574694,"uid":146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:23:09.000Z","msg":"牙朗今晚唔踢"},{"pid":"8c0d001ca88e41d0e60b9319a4c3d37026f48911","tid":574694,"uid":94771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:33:03.000Z","msg":"C朗休戰避「愛」<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=ZavXTvnWBvWBpBSV81nf%2Bcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=2271c149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】周二西甲皇家馬德里作客愛斯賓奴，大紅人基斯坦奴朗拿度再次休戰。<br />\n<br />\n皇馬教練施丹以「人人都要唞」為由，今季不止一次收起葡萄牙猛將基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo），這亦是一星期內第2次讓大紅人輪休，連大軍名單也名落孫山。皇馬上輪以4:0屠殺艾拉維斯，如今面對下游球隊愛斯賓奴，除了C朗缺陣之外，傷兵名單上仍有馬些路、卻奧斯、莫迪歷和捷西斯華利祖。<br />\n<br />\n銀河艦隊公佈的19人名單，隊長沙治奧拉莫斯刑滿復出，連同馬高阿辛斯奧回歸，其他主將包括賓施馬、加里夫巴利、馬約萊爾、盧卡斯華斯基斯、艾斯高、高華錫和卡斯米路等。<br />\n<br />\n連贏5場的皇馬暫以51分排名第3位，落後榜首巴塞多達14分，衛冕希望渺茫，相信本周末聯賽回到主場迎戰基達菲，C朗可望歸隊。"},{"pid":"a687c4318717640ebe13cf519dc0b1ee496b57d4","tid":574694,"uid":173456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c231457f93204ed6370f3a5a85be208ddb92d03","tid":574694,"uid":146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:23:09.000Z","msg":"牙朗今晚唔踢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T16:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓豬柒到"},{"pid":"3b8c75e0278f7e99153b02fefd8310d698b22264","tid":574694,"uid":51951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T23:14:33.000Z","msg":"成日休戰真係好，可以自己揀時間儲到爆氣先入波"},{"pid":"7b256b85136120abdabfb054649f4104698f790c","tid":574694,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b8c75e0278f7e99153b02fefd8310d698b22264","tid":574694,"uid":51951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T23:14:33.000Z","msg":"成日休戰真係好，可以自己揀時間儲到爆氣先入波"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T00:44:28.000Z","msg":"留力對Las Palmas一次入十球爭射手榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93ee79c1db054f60bc91c25f3441c0292c2e134","tid":574694,"uid":36310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b256b85136120abdabfb054649f4104698f790c","tid":574694,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b8c75e0278f7e99153b02fefd8310d698b22264","tid":574694,"uid":51951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T23:14:33.000Z","msg":"成日休戰真係好，可以自己揀時間儲到爆氣先入波"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T00:44:28.000Z","msg":"留力對Las Palmas一次入十球爭射手榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T19:32:44.000Z","msg":"ching sick ball<br />\n今場最少大四喜"}]}